description: Returns a list of all the MatchingWorkflows that have been created for an Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: workflowSummaries
nested_items.description: A list of MatchingWorkflowSummary objects, each of which contain the fields WorkflowName, WorkflowArn, CreatedAt, and UpdatedAt.

nested_items.name: workflowArn
nested_items.description: The ARN (Amazon Resource Name) that Entity Resolution generated for the MatchingWorkflow.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the workflow was created.

nested_items.name: updatedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the workflow was last updated.

nested_items.name: resolutionType
nested_items.description: The method that has been specified for data matching, either using matching provided by Entity Resolution or through a provider service.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token from the previous API call.
